reports.description: Dynamic analysis on Microsoft Windows XP

malicious_activity: Autostart: Registering for autostart using the Windows start menu
Evasion: Ability to check the disk size
Evasion: Ability to detect if Sleep() function is patched
Evasion: Ability to retrieve a list of keyboard layouts
Evasion: Trying to detect analysis virtual environment (timing analysis detection)
Evasion: Trying to enumerate security products installed on the system from WMI
Memory: Replacing the image of a process with the same original executable (potential unpacking)
Steal: Ability to set windows hooks
